rows.label: tlk70000138_04_msg0001
rows.name:
All of Alst stinks of burning thanks
to that Holy Grail.

rows.label: tlk70000138_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Shiya's at the bottom of the Cloud Sea
by now, too... Seems like things'll be
changing around here, and fast.

rows.label: tlk70000138_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Least, that's the sort of rumor you
hear round the ports...

rows.label: tlk70000138_04_msg0004
rows.name:
My dad only cares about his inventions.
Wouldn't have been much skin off my
nose before if he'd dropped dead.

rows.label: tlk70000138_04_msg0005
rows.name:
But I've changed lately. I'm even
starting to think it'd be a good idea to
go check in on him.
